== 反响 ==
菜月昴获得2015-2016年[[Newtype_(杂志)|Newtype Anime Award]]中最佳“角色奖（男性）”<ref name="Newtype Awards">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-10-09/shinkai-your-name-kabaneri-win-top-newtype-anime-awards/.107437|title=Shinkai's 'your name.,' Kabaneri Win Top Newtype Anime Awards|last=Loo|first=Egan|date=2016-10-09|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=2019-08-18}}</ref>。在[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]的投票中，菜月昴以2246票被选为仅次于雷姆的《Re:从零开始的异世界生活》最佳角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.crunchyroll.com/es/anime-feature/2016/09/19/feature-worlds-largest-rezero-character-poll-results-revealed|title=FEATURE: World's Largest Re:ZERO Character Poll Results Revealed|website=Crunchyroll|accessdate=2020-09-10|date=2016-09-19}}</ref>。小林裕介因其配音的菜月昴而获得了{{link-en|Crunchyroll动画奖|Crunchyroll Anime Awards}}的2020年最佳男性声优奖<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2021-02-19/crunchyroll-awards-crown-jujutsu-kaisen-as-anime-of-the-year/.169710|title=Crunchyroll Awards Crown Jujutsu Kaisen as Anime of the Year|website=Anime News Network|accessdate=2021-02-20}}</ref>。

对轻小说中菜月昴的评价，褒贬不一。[[动画新闻网|动画新闻网]]的塞隆·马丁评论了第一卷小说，批评其对话过于冗余；他认为虽然有些对话是为了让菜月昴“令人信服地成为一个傻瓜”，但还是过头了<ref name="Theron Martin 1">{{cite web|first=Theron |last=Martin|title=Re:ZERO Novel 1 – Review|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/re-zero/novel-1/.104935|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=2022-03-17|date=2016-08-04|quote=This brings up the main weakness of the novel: author Tappei Nagatsuki is simply not that good at managing the timing and flow of character dialogue yet. Too many exchanges run overly long, especially the ones that take place in the middle of fight scenes. While some of it is clearly designed to make Subaru convincingly come across as a dork, it's still overdone.}}</ref>。金·莫里西则认为昴的特征是异世界作品的一大亮点，因为他有深深的自我厌恶<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2018-04-13/the-best-isekai-light-novels/.130186|first=Kim |last=Morrissy |title=The Best (and worst) Isekai Light Novels|website=Anime News Network|date=2018-04-13|accessdate=2022-03-17|quote=Some of the best parts of ''Re:Zero'' also involve the protagonist's deep self-loathing, and how going to a fantasy world won't fix his problems.}}</ref>
。

英国动画网（{{lang|en|UK Anime Network}}）的安迪·汉利（{{lang|en|Andy Hanley}}）认为这部作品中最突出的是对时间重置机制（“死亡回归”）的应用，利用多次重温某一特定时期的情节更全面地审视剧中人物，以及探索多次重温无数事件对菜月昴的心理影响，他认为菜月昴是一个非常有缺陷和非常人性化的角色，他的个性和反应非常明显地被他所目睹和参与的事件所染指<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uk-anime.net/articles/Why_Re:ZERO_is_2016's_biggest_hit.html |title=Time looping and character building – why Re:Zero is 2016's biggest hit |last=Hanley |first=Andy|website=UK Anime Network|access-date=2016-07-20 }}</ref>。

